    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance, featuring the high-revving S65 V8 engine equipped with eight individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The power is managed by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox, sending torque through a speed-sensitive M Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, utilizing aluminum multi-link suspension geometry that delivers exceptional tactile feedback. Maintenance is current, with critical preventative services\u2014including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator updates\u2014already performed to ensure the longevity of the high-performance internals. This is a mechanically robust example of BMW\u2019s finest engineering era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
