    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of pride in ownership, offering a balanced blend of reliability and style. The exterior paint maintains a high-gloss finish, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and light surface scratches near the door handles, typical of a well-loved car. Inside, the interior is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the seats are supportive with no rips or thinning, and all electronic features\u2014including the premium audio system and dual-zone climate control\u2014operate exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers smooth power, backed by a complete service history of regular oil changes and recent brake pad replacements. The tires are in great shape with deep tread remaining, and the suspension provides a comfortable, rattle-free ride. This car is ready for immediate use and represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, attractive vehicle that has been treated with respect.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
