      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies the perfect balance of performance and aesthetic refinement. This unit has undergone a comprehensive professional inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and roadworthiness. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain, this vehicle offers a sophisticated driving experience and exceptional long-term value. It stands as a testament to diligent ownership and remains an exemplary choice for the discerning buyer.",
      "price": 36850.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
