      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? I'm selling my car, and it's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape, runs smoothly, and has been well-loved and taken care of over the years. It's perfect for zipping around town or hitting the open road for a weekend getaway. I'd love for it to go to a great new home\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
