      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical configuration includes a functional M-Variable Differential Lock and a chassis that remains taut thanks to recent bushing refreshes. The double-VANOS system has been serviced to maintain timing precision, and the rear subframe has been inspected for structural integrity. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the car remains an exceptional performer with sharp turn-in and balanced weight distribution. Ideal for the enthusiast seeking a mechanically sound icon that is ready for the open road.",
